"A crucial part of the business is to transform prospects into customers, "
"then to follow up efficiently on the mission and finally to bill customers "
"in for your work. We got you covered all along this journey!"
msgstr ""
"Une autre part essentielle de l’activité est de transformer les prospects en "
"clients, puis de suivre efficacement la mission, pour enfin facturer vos "
"clients. Nous vous accompagnons tout au long de ce parcours !"

